    Authoring rules honored (per AAP Sections 0.7.1 / 0.7.2 and the
    agent prompt's eight authoring rules):

      Rule 1 - Synthetic only (AAP Section 0.7.2 NO-PII clause):
        subject = "Demo task 06: Complaint investigation"
                  (synthetic identifier using the literal word "Demo"
                   plus a numeral plus a generic agent-action phrase
                   "Complaint investigation"; "Complaint" is a generic
                   case-type label per AAP Section 0.5.7's case_type
                   choice list, NOT a real complaint or person's name;
