      Rule 2 - Choice value precision (CRITICAL FOR THIS TASK):
        type   = "Investigation"  (exactly as registered in
                  ../../choices/sys_choice_case_task_type.xml; the first
                  of the four task types - Investigation, Review,
                  Follow-up, Other; capital I deliberate -
                  "Investigation" not "investigation" or
                  "INVESTIGATION"; semantically pairs with task 07's
                  Investigation type, reflecting that both tasks on
                  case 08 are investigation-related activities on the
                  same Complaint case)
        status = "In Progress"  (exactly as registered in
                  ../../choices/sys_choice_case_task_status.xml; the
                  middle of the three task statuses - Open, In Progress,
                  Closed; SINGLE SPACE between the two words; capital
                  I and capital P deliberate - "In Progress" NOT
                  "InProgress" (no separator), NOT "In_Progress"
                  (underscore), NOT "in progress" (lowercase), NOT
                  "IN PROGRESS" (all uppercase), NOT "In  Progress"
